1.To Create an Archive Of The dirx Directory And Save It as dirxtar.tar

# tar -cvf mumbai.tar mumbai

2. For Compressing and Making a Zip File

# gzip mumbai.tar

3. For Checking This Zip File

# ls -l

(output)
mumbai.tar.gz

4. For Making Unzip File (Removing) Gz

# gunzip mumbai.tar.gz

5. To Extract the contents of .Tar File

# tar -xvf mumbai.tar
